title: Grateful Dead Live at Miami Arena on 1994-04-06
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Jack A Roe, Wang Dang Doodle, Broken Arrow, West L.A. Fadeaway, El Paso*, Row Jimmy, Promised Land

Set 2

Here Comes Sunshine, Samson & Delilah, Cumberland Blues, Way to Go Home, Women Are Smarter, Drums-> Space-> The Wheel, All Along The Watchtower, Standing On the Moon, E: Johnny B. Goode

* Weir on acoustic

reviews.review_text:
I am on an amazing journey I am listening to every 1994 show in order, mining for gold. 

Pretty average show in a terrible venue/part of town/state. Outstanding setlist though. Phil kicks ass as usual (Broken Arrow) and we do get a West LA Fadeaway. The Wheel has a cool intro out of Space.
